{"tid":1523054,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"太子721翻版 死黑警打市民","createTime":"2019-08-31T15:16:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-31T15:56:56.000Z","uid":200493,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"ff1d9fb72ade1bcc5ce8b31bec938868ba160f66","tid":1523054,"uid":200493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T15:16:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5KZ4WGE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5KZ4WGE.jpg&h=ee36058c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【23:00】警方速龍小隊衝入太子站一架列車車廂，制服多人，並向無任何裝備的市民不停揮棍，及噴射胡椒水。<br />\n<br />\n月台上有被捕者頭部流血。警察入車廂後，有市民甚為驚惶，跪地要求警察停止，但警察繼續射胡椒噴霧，市民狀甚痛苦，相擁而哭。<br />\n<br />\n（無綫新聞截圖）<br />\n <br />\n✽ㅤ✽ㅤ✽<br />\nㅤ<br />\n《立場新聞》<br />\n直播專頁：<a href=\"https://live.thestandnews.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Flive.thestandnews.com%2F&d=30ZlKbyCH33W3wkrfz60CyUaeeTarj8%2BpjPG%2B7PQGFg%3D&h=a0c39b6e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Flive.thestandnews.com%2F&h=abb76194\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://live.thestandnews.com/</a>"},{"pid":"379d992793bd550565adb820dd41aaf09eb3ce32","tid":1523054,"uid":219429,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T15:20:14.000Z","msg":"畜生到不如<br />\n狗鐵係幫兇"},{"pid":"1eb2ed51072f2644f9a97ba5332d66681013a549","tid":1523054,"uid":50904,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T15:21:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZANigH1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZANigH1.jpg&h=2d44cc56&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aDFr922.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaDFr922.jpg&h=1381cd3e&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n東方live岩先影住，打爆左同一卡車兩個人個頭，成地血<br />\n仲要10幾分鐘都無救護員"},{"pid":"0544d0369b26f2ef232408e3243520d6be9e5ced","tid":1523054,"uid":50904,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T15:22:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.y